### Preamble  

The Nevron Public License (NPL) is designed to provide freedom to use, share, modify, and redistribute the Nevron AI agent and its associated works while ensuring proper attribution to the project and its creators. This license promotes innovation and collaboration by allowing commercial and non-commercial uses of Nevron, as long as the attribution requirements are fulfilled.  

The intent is to protect the rights of creators while empowering users to adapt and enhance the project for their own purposes, ensuring that all derived works continue to acknowledge the original contributions.  

